text: Robert Finch may refer to: * Robert Finch (American politician) (1925–1995), Republican politician from California * Robert Finch (antiquarian) (1783–1830), English antiquary * Robert Finch (Lord Mayor) (1944–2016), British politician and lawyer * Robert Finch (nature writer) (born 1943), American nature writer and essayist * Robert Finch (poet) (1900–1995), Canadian poet and academic * Robert Finch (priest) (1724–1803), English divine * Robert Finch (rugby league) (born 1955), Australian rugby league player * Bob Finch (born 1954), British coal trader and businessman * Bobby Finch (c. 1948–1978), English footballer ==See also== * Finch (surname)
